    citation-twoiaf-andal-invasion:
        source: source-twoiaf
        properties:
            locator: "Ancient History: The Arrival of the Andals"
            accessed: "2026-03-06"
        notes: "The Andal invasion of Westeros: origin in Andalos, iron weapons, conquest of the Vale and riverlands, Erreg the Kinslayer at High Heart, Urron Redhand and the Iron Islands. Hugor of the Hill and the Seven-Pointed Star."
